-title-size-two" style="--awb-margin-bottom:20px;--awb-font-size:24px;"><h2 class="fusion-title-heading title-heading-center fusion-responsive-typography-calculated" style="font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-style:normal;font-weight:400;margin:0;font-size:1em;--fontSize:24;line-height:1.5;"><p style="text-align: center;">产品包装定做FAQ</p></h2></div></div></div><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-12 fusion_builder_column_1_2 1_2 fusion-flex-column" style="--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:50%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:3.84%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:0px;--awb-spacing-left-large:3.84%;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column"><div class="accordian fusion-accordian" style="--awb-border-size:2px;--awb-icon-size:16px;--awb-content-font-size:16px;--awb-icon-alignment:left;--awb-hover-color:#ffffff;--awb-border-color:#cfa074;--awb-background-color:#ffffff;--awb-divider-color:#e0dede;--awb-divider-hover-color:#e0dede;--awb-icon-color:#cfa074;--awb-title-color:#262626;--awb-content-color:#545454;--awb-icon-box-color:#cfa074;--awb-toggle-hover-accent-color:#cfa074;--awb-title-font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;--awb-title-font-weight:400;--awb-title-font-style:normal;--awb-content-font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;--awb-content-font-style:normal;--awb-content-font-weight:400;"><div class="panel-group fusion-toggle-icon-unboxed" id="accordion-181-1"><div class="fusion-panel panel-default panel-e0009a6bbac54e067 fusion-toggle-no-divider fusion-toggle-boxed-mode"><div class="panel-heading"><h4 class="panel-title toggle" id="toggle_e0009a6bbac54e067"><a aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="e0009a6bbac54e067" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#e0009a6bbac54e067" href="#e0009a6bbac54e067"><span class="fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fa-fusion-box active-icon awb-icon-minus" aria-hidden="true"></i><i class="fa-fusion-box inactive-icon awb-icon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><span class="fusion-toggle-heading">包装的价格多少？</span></a></h4></div><div id="e0009a6bbac54e067" class="panel-collapse collapse " aria-labelledby="toggle_e0009a6bbac54e067"><div class="panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix">
<p>由于包装产品的不确定性,涉及到设计,材质,工艺,尺寸等各方面因素，价格都不是固定的,需要我们的业务人员根据您的具体需求来计算的. 您可以联系我们的在线客服进行初步了解.</p>
</div></div></div><div class="fusion-panel panel-default panel-ec34f7678aef69b06 fusion-toggle-no-divider fusion-toggle-boxed-mode"><div class="panel-heading"><h4 class="panel-title toggle" id="toggle_ec34f7678aef69b06"><a aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="ec34f7678aef69b06" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#ec34f7678aef69b06" href="#ec34f7678aef69b06"><span class="fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fa-fusion-box active-icon awb-icon-minus" aria-hidden="true"></i><i class="fa-fusion-box inactive-icon awb-icon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><span class="fusion-toggle-heading">包装盒或手提袋能够打样吗？</span></a></h4></div><div id="ec34f7678aef69b06" class="panel-collapse collapse " aria-labelledby="toggle_ec34f7678aef69b06"><div class="panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix">
<p>可以的，我们可以按照客户的图稿，设计，实样，进行打成品样。样品主要分为成品样(完全按照设计要求的实现产品)和白样(不含任何工艺,只有结构). 样品需要收取一定的样品费用，具体价格需要参考包装工艺。在订单数量达到起订量后，样品费可退还。</p>
</div></div></div><div class="fusion-panel panel-default panel-ef387c82ef9fc42a5 fusion-toggle-no-divider fusion-toggle-boxed-mode"><div class="panel-heading"><h4 class="panel-title toggle" id="toggle_ef387c82ef9fc42a5"><a aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="ef387c82ef9fc42a5" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#ef387c82ef9fc42a5" href="#ef387c82ef9fc42a5"><span class="fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fa-fusion-box active-icon awb-icon-minus" aria-hidden="true"></i><i class="fa-fusion-box inactive-icon awb-icon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><span class="fusion-toggle-heading">包装打样周期和生产周期是多少？ </span></a></h4></div><div id="ef387c82ef9fc42a5" class="panel-collapse collapse " aria-labelledby="toggle_ef387c82ef9fc42a5"><div class="panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix">
<p>打样周期是3~7天<br />
具体时间:需要根据包装的工艺要求，涉及的有(结构，印刷，烫金，压纹)等各个方面的工艺,有些工艺需要开模具,需要消耗一定的时间期限.<br />
生产周期在20~30天。</p>
</div></div></div><div class="fusion-panel panel-default panel-6ba9a44e98e69d7b2 fusion-toggle-no-divider fusion-toggle-boxed-mode"><div class="panel-heading"><h4 class="panel-title toggle" id="toggle_6ba9a44e98e69d7b2"><a aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="6ba9a44e98e69d7b2" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#6ba9a44e98e69d7b2" href="#6ba9a44e98e69d7b2"><span class="fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fa-fusion-box active-icon awb-icon-minus" aria-hidden="true"></i><i class="fa-fusion-box inactive-icon awb-icon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><span class="fusion-toggle-heading">你们定做哪些产品包装</span></a></h4></div><div id="6ba9a44e98e69d7b2" class="panel-collapse collapse " aria-labelledby="toggle_6ba9a44e98e69d7b2"><div class="panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix">
<p>我们的包装盒与手提袋产品不限制产品，适用化妆品,珠宝,礼品,电子产品,服装,奢侈品,配饰,保健食品, 茶叶红酒等&#8230;在包装行业沉浸了20余年,接触到了各个行业的产品包装盒定做,能够给到客户相应的建议与见解.</p>
</div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="fusion-layout-column fusion_builder_column fusion-builder-column-13 fusion_builder_column_1_2 1_2 fusion-flex-column" style="--awb-bg-size:cover;--awb-width-large:50%;--awb-margin-top-large:0px;--awb-spacing-right-large:3.84%;--awb-margin-bottom-large:0px;--awb-spacing-left-large:3.84%;--awb-width-medium:100%;--awb-order-medium:0;--awb-spacing-right-medium:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-medium:1.92%;--awb-width-small:100%;--awb-order-small:0;--awb-spacing-right-small:1.92%;--awb-spacing-left-small:1.92%;"><div class="fusion-column-wrapper fusion-column-has-shadow fusion-flex-justify-content-flex-start fusion-content-layout-column"><div class="accordian fusion-accordian" style="--awb-border-size:2px;--awb-icon-size:16px;--awb-content-font-size:16px;--awb-icon-alignment:left;--awb-hover-color:#ffffff;--awb-border-color:#cfa074;--awb-background-color:#ffffff;--awb-divider-color:#e0dede;--awb-divider-hover-color:#e0dede;--awb-icon-color:#cfa074;--awb-title-color:#262626;--awb-content-color:#545454;--awb-icon-box-color:#cfa074;--awb-toggle-hover-accent-color:#cfa074;--awb-title-font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;--awb-title-font-weight:400;--awb-title-font-style:normal;--awb-content-font-family:Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;--awb-content-font-style:normal;--awb-content-font-weight:400;"><div class="panel-group fusion-toggle-icon-unboxed" id="accordion-181-2"><div class="fusion-panel panel-default panel-ab0c2ac3fd85a1c9b fusion-toggle-no-divider fusion-toggle-boxed-mode"><div class="panel-heading"><h4 class="panel-title toggle" id="toggle_ab0c2ac3fd85a1c9b"><a aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="ab0c2ac3fd85a1c9b" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#ab0c2ac3fd85a1c9b" href="#ab0c2ac3fd85a1c9b"><span class="fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fa-fusion-box active-icon awb-icon-minus" aria-hidden="true"></i><i class="fa-fusion-box inactive-icon awb-icon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><span class="fusion-toggle-heading">你们是厂家吗？</span></a></h4></div><div id="ab0c2ac3fd85a1c9b" class="panel-collapse collapse " aria-labelledby="toggle_ab0c2ac3fd85a1c9b"><div class="panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix">
<p>我们是包装盒生产厂家，欣派自1997年开始从事包装贸易出口，从最初的美国市场，辐射到欧洲，到如今在各个大洲都有着稳定的客户群体。凭借的是我们精湛的做工与严谨的态度。工厂占地10000平方米。采用流水线包装设备机械化生产，200余人的熟练操作工生产团队。</p>
</div></div></div><div class="fusion-panel panel-default panel-54a734984404a6b32 fusion-toggle-no-divider fusion-toggle-boxed-mode"><div class="panel-heading"><h4 class="panel-title toggle" id="toggle_54a734984404a6b32"><a aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="54a734984404a6b32" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#54a734984404a6b32" href="#54a734984404a6b32"><span class="fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fa-fusion-box active-icon awb-icon-minus" aria-hidden="true"></i><i class="fa-fusion-box inactive-icon awb-icon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><span class="fusion-toggle-heading"> 你们有什么资质认证吗？</span></a></h4></div><div id="54a734984404a6b32" class="panel-collapse collapse " aria-labelledby="toggle_54a734984404a6b32"><div class="panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix">
<p>欣派常年为欧美奢侈品牌提供包装定制服务，生产定做的包装盒与手提袋完全符合欧盟相关认证标准。例: FSC(森林环保认证,环保包装)，ISO-9001(产品质量管理体系)，ISO-14001(环境管理体系认证)，Sedex(供应商商业道德认证)，奢侈品牌第二方验厂报告等&#8230;</p>
</div></div></div><div class="fusion-panel panel-default panel-5d2b51701e00b607f fusion-toggle-no-divider fusion-toggle-boxed-mode"><div class="panel-heading"><h4 class="panel-title toggle" id="toggle_5d2b51701e00b607f"><a aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="5d2b51701e00b607f" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#5d2b51701e00b607f" href="#5d2b51701e00b607f"><span class="fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fa-fusion-box active-icon awb-icon-minus" aria-hidden="true"></i><i class="fa-fusion-box inactive-icon awb-icon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><span class="fusion-toggle-heading">你们能做包装设计吗？</span></a></h4></div><div id="5d2b51701e00b607f" class="panel-collapse collapse " aria-labelledby="toggle_5d2b51701e00b607f"><div class="panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix">
<p>我们能做简单的结构设计，在我们现有的盒型上更改下LOGO，其他基本不变是可以的。如果是从无到有的平面设计，这种我们不是特别擅长，需要设计公司来做。每个公司都有每个公司的企业文化，设计方面最好由公司的设计部门来做，更能契合品牌文化。我们相应的能够提供相关的建议与实现难度，我们是工厂主要负责生产制作。</p>
</div></div></div><div class="fusion-panel panel-default panel-9cd113d3582b5fb24 fusion-toggle-no-divider fusion-toggle-boxed-mode"><div class="panel-heading"><h4 class="panel-title toggle" id="toggle_9cd113d3582b5fb24"><a aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="9cd113d3582b5fb24" role="button" data-toggle="collapse" data-target="#9cd113d3582b5fb24" href="#9cd113d3582b5fb24"><span class="fusion-toggle-icon-wrapper" aria-hidden="true"><i class="fa-fusion-box active-icon awb-icon-minus" aria-hidden="true"></i><i class="fa-fusion-box inactive-icon awb-icon-plus" aria-hidden="true"></i></span><span class="fusion-toggle-heading">你们做过哪些品牌</span></a></h4></div><div id="9cd113d3582b5fb24" class="panel-collapse collapse " aria-labelledby="toggle_9cd113d3582b5fb24"><div class="panel-body toggle-content fusion-clearfix">
<p>欣派自1997年开始从事包装盒定制业务,出口了20多年,客户遍布全球.欧美地区的奢侈品牌我们做过很多并且长期合作中. 因为涉及保密协议,我们不能对外宣传。如果你想了解我们做了哪些奢侈品牌,可以联系我们.</p>
